com\/article\/2015\/01\/15\/us-apple-google-lawsuit-idUSKBN0KO2RG20150115\"><em>avoid poaching<\/em><\/a> each other&#8217;s employees.<\/p>\n<p>The A123 suit has drawn <a href=\"http:\/\/www.techmeme.com\/150218\/p34#a150218p34\">outsize attention<\/a> because the five missing employees were reportedly working on automotive batteries, adding fuel to the <a href=\"http:\/\/fortune.com\/2015\/02\/12\/about-that-apple-self-driving-car\/\">Apple car rumor<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Follow Philip Elmer-DeWitt on Twitter at <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/philiped\"><span class=\"s2\">@philiped<\/span><\/a>. Read his Apple <a href=\"http:\/\/fortune.com\/company\/aapl\/\"><span class=\"s2\">AAPL<\/span><\/a> coverage at <a href=\"http:\/\/fortune.com\/ped\"><span class=\"s2\">fortune.com\/ped<\/span><\/a> or subscribe via his <a href=\"http:\/\/feeds.feedburner.com\/philip-elmer-dewitt\"><span class=\"s2\">RSS feed<\/span><\/a>.<\/span><\/p>\n","time":{"pretty":"February 19, 2015","published":"2015-02-19 06:59:11","updated":"2015-02-19 06:59:11","minute":"6:59 AM EST","is_same_day":true,"is_home_pop":true},"comment_url":"http:\/\/fortune.com\/2015\/02\/19\/apple-sued-when-it-poaches-sued-when-it-doesnt\/","absolute_url":"http:\/\/fortune.com\/2015\/02\/19\/apple-sued-when-it-poaches-sued-when-it-doesnt\/","redirect_url":"","partner":"","outbrain_url":"http:\/\/fortune.com\/2015\/02\/19\/apple-sued-when-it-poaches-sued-when-it-doesnt\/","outbrain_footer":true,"outbrain_right_rail":false,"short_title":"Apple: Sued when it poaches. Sued when it doesn't.","post_type":"post","featured_type":"image","featured_image":{"src":"https:\/\/fortunedotcom.files.wordpress.com\/2015\/02\/1-infinite-loop.png?w=840&h=485&crop=1","class":"featured-img-article_full","credit":"Wikicommons","caption":"","attach_id":"996999"},"excerpt":"<p>Ah, the irony.\u00a0<\/p>\n","authors":[{"id":"273153","url":"http:\/\/fortune.com\/author\/philip-elmer-dewitt\/","name":"Philip Elmer